entity.mountainmobs.jabberwock.name=Jabberwock
entity.mountainmobs.jabberwock.description=Vicious deer like creatures, their hooked claws will cause a weight effect pulling their victim down, this prevents any jumping and increases falling damage, making Jabberwocks deadly in the mountains.
achievement.jabberwock.kill=The Jaws That Bite!
achievement.jabberwock.kill.desc=Slay a Jabberwock.
achievement.jabberwock.learn=The Claws That Catch!
achievement.jabberwock.learn.desc=Add a Jabberwock to your Beastiary.
achievement.jabberwock.summon=The Mome Raths Outgrabe!
achievement.jabberwock.summon.desc=Summon a Jabberwock.
entity.mountainmobs.troll.name=Troll
entity.mountainmobs.troll.description=In the sun a Trolls skin is as hard as stone giving them good defense. Out of the sun their they soften increasing their speed but lowering their defense. They will destroy soft blocks if you get close.
achievement.troll.kill=Hohoho Hoo Hooh!
achievement.troll.kill.desc=Slay a Troll.
achievement.troll.learn=Of Flesh and Stone!
achievement.troll.learn.desc=Add a Troll to your Beastiary.
entity.mountainmobs.yale.name=Yale
entity.mountainmobs.yale.description=Strange fluffy ram-like creatures. Yales provide wool which can be obtained using shears, they can also be farmed with vegetables. They use their horns as front legs and eat with tiny arms.
achievement.yale.kill=Poor Sheep Thingy!
achievement.yale.kill.desc=Slay a Yale.
achievement.yale.learn=Front Horn Legs?
achievement.yale.learn.desc=Add a Yale to your Beastiary.
entity.mountainmobs.geonach.name=Geonach
entity.mountainmobs.geonach.description=Geonachs are brutal earth elementals commonly found by unsuspecting miners when disturbing the earth. They rapidly strike twice with a dig slowdown spear and then slam with their weight debuff fist.
achievement.geonach.kill=Rock and Roll!
achievement.geonach.kill.desc=Slay a Geonach.
achievement.geonach.learn=Rock Elemental
achievement.geonach.learn.desc=Add a Geonach to your Beastiary.
achievement.geonach.summon=Geomancy 101
achievement.geonach.summon.desc=Summon a Geonach.
entity.mountainmobs.beholder.name=Beholder
entity.mountainmobs.beholder.description=Large hostile masses of eyes and tentacles with an eternal hunger for magic energy! Beholders are known to fire a deadly laser storm of arcane energy to defeat their foes.
achievement.beholder.kill=Eye Poker
achievement.beholder.kill.desc=Slay a Beholder.
achievement.beholder.learn=Magic Eaters!
achievement.beholder.learn.desc=Add a Beholder to your Beastiary.
achievement.beholder.summon=Behold!
achievement.beholder.summon.desc=Summon a Beholder.
entity.mountainmobs.barghest.name=Barghest
entity.mountainmobs.barghest.description=Deadly mountian predators capable of making high leaps with deadly weight attacks on impact. Barghests are also very competent climbers making them exceptional mounts for the mountains.
achievement.barghest.kill=Primal Hunting
achievement.barghest.kill.desc=Slay a Barghest.
achievement.barghest.learn=Magic Eaters!
achievement.barghest.learn.desc=Add a Barghest to your Beastiary.
achievement.barghest.tame=Stripes Are In!
achievement.barghest.tame.desc=Tame a Barghest.
